author: KetteKaiser
body:
>	if Trump deescalates

I think that given what we know of ol’Dorito Mussolini, he won’t calm it down. I’d love it to happen that way, but he has the political finesse of a dog being fucked on roller skates*.
Couple that with the fact that all the adults have left the room; I don’t see it being pretty. 
US shale is solid so I can’t imagine oil jumping up that much.
The defense contractors to watch are:

-	LMT
-	RTN
-	KTOS
-	LHX
-	ARNC
-	TDY
-	TDG
-	GD (Merging w/RTN this year)

Maybe GLD will get a bump, same for CLR

Really gotta start watching those media companies though. Ad sales at going to be astronomical leading up to the Primary.
Sinclair, Nexstar, Grey, those OTT shills too.

*”Waystar Royco, Feel It.”
